{"tid":1742193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《喱騷》特備節目：今宵多珍重","createTime":"2019-11-20T16:17:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T16:44:13.000Z","uid":38279,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d9a43ea60a25f69c95ddf2767c364bc376d73c94","tid":1742193,"uid":38279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:17:17.000Z","msg":"由六月開始，香港人嘅問候句都變成問對方safe唔safe... 原來能夠平安返屋企，都係一件非常值得感恩嘅事。<br />\n年輕人，究竟有咩驅使你三更半夜，都喺條街度唔肯走？係愛呀？定係責任呢？每一晚望住手機，我哋只有一個願望，就係佢哋每一個都平平安安返屋企。今晚CEO就同三位大學生促膝詳談，希望聽下佢哋嘅心聲、關心佢哋嘅想法，今宵多珍重。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/c6IOIt_zJE4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fc6IOIt_zJE4&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=4f3cf6bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/c6IOIt_zJE4</a>"},{"pid":"40c149fa3e141bce1cc40c33e38b771af2e1468f","tid":1742193,"uid":278990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:40:26.000Z","msg":"喊到仆街"},{"pid":"898b411ee15c2e8e2e6ab26497bed3a0e3ff4f51","tid":1742193,"uid":29370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:43:35.000Z","msg":"啲眼淚係咁流"},{"pid":"2254ec8b53da79919af8e1ea6f2d703027a01589","tid":1742193,"uid":306826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:44:13.000Z","msg":"阻你地少少時間 有關選舉問題可以睇以下post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n0成本截斷建制藍絲收入 (下)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1742026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1742026</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}